title: SPY Presents: John John Florence
description: Introducing the John John Signature Kubrik. ROCK ON THE ROCK. Inspired by classic rock and life on The Rock, John John's signature Kubrik features a matte black frame, matte grey temples with gunmetal accents and bold black mirror lens.
